/p>","South Holland and The Deepings","Mr John Hayes","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/657977/answer",,,,,"57431","2016-12-16T10:52:57.767Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/657977/answer","Biography information for Sir John Hayes","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/657977/answer",,,,,"27","Transport","Transport","2016-12-13","Large Goods Vehicles","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Transport, with reference to the evaluation of the longer semi-trailer trial; annual report 2015, published in August 2016, what independent research has been carried out on the crashes and incidents affecting longer semi-trailers that were logged in the September 2016 trial report.","false","Biography information for Pat Glass","North West Durham","Pat Glass","57442"
